        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="51" value="&lt;b&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#3b82f6&quot;&gt;🔗 Cross-Service HTTP Calls via axios&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;[Exam Service :3003]  ——  GET /api/students/:id  ——▶  [Student Service :3001]  ·  Validate student exists before creating exam entry&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;[Transcript Service :3005]  ——  GET /api/students/:id  ——▶  [Student Service :3001]  ·  Fetch student profile for transcript&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;[Transcript Service :3005]  ——  GET /api/results/student/:id  ——▶  [Result Service :3004]  ·  Fetch semester results and GPA for transcript"
          style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#3b82f6;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;arcSize=3;"
          vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="27" y="610" width="1600" height="95" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

